@node "Thanks" "Control Panel Guide - Thanks"
@{b}@{u}Thanks... @{ub}@{uu}
Thanks to everybody who helped with suggestions on improving Control Panel.

Thanks also to everybody who registered Control Panel 4.

Finally I thank everybody who's arexx scripts and arexx libraries which have
helped me to get to grips with this particular language.

I particularly thank everybody who supports shareware and particularly those
